---
import Layout from '../layouts/layout.astro'
import {Image} from 'astro:assets'
import profileImage from '../assets/pfp.png'

const title = 'About Soham Sarkar | Tech Enthusiast & App Developer'
const description =
  "Learn about Soham Sarkar's journey, philosophy, and approach to building innovative and user-centric applications."
---

<Layout content={{title, description}}>
  <main class='about-page'>
    <h1>About Soham Sarkar</h1>

    <section class='profile'>
      <Image src={profileImage} alt='Soham Sarkar' width={300} height={300} />
      <div>
        <h2>Tech Enthusiast, Problem Solver, and App Developer</h2>
        <p>
          Hello! I'm Soham Sarkar, a passionate app developer based in Bangalore, India. With a
          diverse background spanning technology, product development, sales, marketing, and
          problem-solving, I bring a unique perspective to every project I undertake.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>My Journey</h2>
      <p>
        My journey in the tech world began with a simple realization: technology has the power to
        solve real-world problems. This insight has guided my career and shaped my approach to app
        development. From my early days of coding to my current role as a full-stack developer, I've
        always been driven by the desire to create solutions that make a tangible difference in
        people's lives.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>My Philosophy on Building Apps</h2>

      <h3>Solving Real Problems Through Personal Experience</h3>
      <p>
        At the heart of my development process is a simple yet powerful philosophy: <strong
          >I build apps to solve problems I've personally encountered</strong
        >. This approach ensures that every application I create is:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Rooted in real-world needs</li>
        <li>Designed with genuine user empathy</li>
        <li>Practical and immediately useful</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        By addressing challenges I've faced firsthand, I can anticipate user needs more effectively
        and create solutions that resonate on a personal level.
      </p>

      <h3>Leveraging Diverse Expertise</h3>
      <p>My multifaceted background allows me to approach app development from various angles:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Technology:</strong> Staying at the forefront of coding languages and development frameworks
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Product Development:</strong> Crafting user-centric products that meet market needs
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Sales and Marketing:</strong> Understanding how to position and promote apps effectively
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Problem-Solving:</strong> Approaching challenges with creativity and analytical thinking
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h3>A Deep Commitment to Design Excellence</h3>
      <p>
        I believe that <strong
          >great design is the cornerstone of every successful application</strong
        >. My commitment to design excellence encompasses:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Efficiency:</strong> Creating apps that perform seamlessly with quick load times
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Intuitive User Experience:</strong> Designing interfaces that are easy to navigate
          and enjoyable to use
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Attention to Detail:</strong> Meticulously refining every element for a polished result
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Performance Optimization:</strong> Leveraging cutting-edge technologies for speed and
          responsiveness
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Accessibility:</strong> Ensuring apps are usable for people with varying abilities
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Let's Connect</h2>
      <p>
        I'm always excited to take on new challenges and collaborate on innovative projects. Whether
        you have a specific app idea in mind or just want to discuss the latest in tech, I'd love to
        hear from you.
      </p>
      <p>
        Feel free to explore my projects and learn more about my work right here on my website. If
        you'd like to connect, don't hesitate to reach out through any of the social links below or
        drop me an email.
      </p>
      <p>Thank you for visiting my digital space. Let's build something amazing together!</p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    color: #fff;
    font-family: 'Victor Mono', monospace;
  }

  h1,
  h2,
  h3 {
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  p {
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .profile {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .profile img {
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  ul {
    list-style-type: none;
    padding-left: 1rem;
  }

  ul li::before {
    content: 'â€¢';
    color: #4a90e2;
    font-weight: bold;
    display: inline-block;
    width: 1em;
    margin-left: -1em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .profile {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    h3 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
